Lde/ecspride/FieldSensitivity2;->onCreat: The method Lde/ecspride/FieldSensitivity2;->onCreate:(Landroid/os/Bundle;)V involves the creation of a Datacontainer object, setting its description to 'abc', retrieving and using the SIM serial number from the TelephonyManager service for setting the secret in the Datacontainer, and sending an SMS message with the description as content. The SIM serial number is considered sensitive information.
